  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The length of each side of a square is <math alttext=\"94\"><mn>94</mn></math> centimeters (cm). Which expression gives the area, in <math alttext=\"c m squared\"><msup><mi>cm</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>, of the square?</p>",
